WEBVTT

01:37.900 --> 01:41.020
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.090 --> 01:43.920
[Episode 20]

01:46.310 --> 01:47.310
When will it open?

01:50.840 --> 01:51.920
Very soon.

02:05.400 --> 02:06.480
With such good news,

02:06.480 --> 02:07.590
why didn't you inform me?

02:07.590 --> 02:08.120
Mr. Duan.

02:08.280 --> 02:08.960
Ms. Xu.

02:09.520 --> 02:10.370
Mr. Xue.

02:10.710 --> 02:11.390
Chef Li.

02:12.280 --> 02:12.940
Mr. Ji.

02:13.090 --> 02:15.350
This is quite a fresh combination today.

02:18.310 --> 02:19.680
I've long heard that

02:20.100 --> 02:23.980
Chef Li has been working on
the recipe of Yan Du Xian.

02:24.590 --> 02:26.550
Now that I've seen this dish today,

02:26.750 --> 02:28.810
I wonder if I have the luck to taste it.

02:31.450 --> 02:33.170
Yes, yes, yes.

02:34.550 --> 02:35.320
Let me do it.

02:40.430 --> 02:41.360
Taste it now.

02:41.630 --> 02:42.079
Okay.

02:42.079 --> 02:43.280
Be careful. It's hot.

02:55.040 --> 02:56.720
What do you think, Mr. Duan?

02:59.020 --> 03:00.480
It's kind of interesting.

03:02.190 --> 03:02.970
Mr. Ji.

03:03.400 --> 03:04.620
When the restaurant opens,

03:04.620 --> 03:05.910
save a few tables for me.

03:05.910 --> 03:08.570
I'll come support
the Chinese restaurant, too.

03:09.000 --> 03:10.470
Mr. Duan,
if you visit our Chinese restaurant,

03:10.470 --> 03:12.190
how could a few tables be enough?

03:12.190 --> 03:14.370
All our private rooms on the third floor
will be reserved for you.

03:14.370 --> 03:15.030
Okay.

03:15.470 --> 03:16.030
As for the people,

03:16.030 --> 03:17.400
you can have as many as you want.

03:17.400 --> 03:18.740
But when it comes to the reputation,

03:18.740 --> 03:20.340
you have to earn it yourself.

03:22.920 --> 03:23.600
Of course.

03:26.480 --> 03:27.120
Mr. Duan.

03:27.680 --> 03:29.050
Chef Jia is asking...

03:29.470 --> 03:30.120
Um...

03:30.140 --> 03:31.400
Tell him not to worry.

03:31.910 --> 03:32.470
I won't

03:32.470 --> 03:34.470
give the Purong Chinese Restaurant

03:34.470 --> 03:36.329
any chance to turn things around.

03:37.710 --> 03:39.570
When will their restaurant open?

03:40.870 --> 03:42.550
On the 18th of this month.

03:44.870 --> 03:48.600
Let's just make it shut down
on the opening day of their restaurant.

03:53.710 --> 03:54.560
It's almost ready.

03:54.560 --> 03:55.890
I think we can eat it now.

03:57.400 --> 03:58.800
We are having a special meal here

03:58.800 --> 04:00.360
without inviting Mr. Xue.

04:00.360 --> 04:01.520
Will he be unhappy?

04:02.790 --> 04:03.950
Who cares about him?

04:04.030 --> 04:06.090
This is a gathering between us girls.

04:07.150 --> 04:08.240
Here. Be careful. It's hot.

04:08.240 --> 04:08.710
Okay.

04:08.710 --> 04:09.240
It's hot.

04:16.070 --> 04:17.579
Confess and you will be treated leniently.

04:17.579 --> 04:20.040
Did something happen
between you and Mr. Ji?

04:23.050 --> 04:24.480
Nothing happened.

04:25.390 --> 04:26.260
No.

04:26.600 --> 04:27.600
Why do I feel that

04:27.600 --> 04:29.490
since we came back from our hometown,

04:29.490 --> 04:31.950
the vibe between you two
has been different?

04:32.250 --> 04:35.130
Vibe? What vibe?

04:36.720 --> 04:38.870
A guilty vibe.

04:39.560 --> 04:40.560
Tell me the truth.

04:41.070 --> 04:43.159
What is the hidden story between you two

04:43.159 --> 04:44.690
that you can't even tell me?

04:46.590 --> 04:48.520
This sweet potato is so delicious.

04:48.790 --> 04:49.740
Taste it now.

04:49.770 --> 04:51.370
Stop changing the subject.

04:53.630 --> 04:54.409
How about this?

04:54.409 --> 04:55.670
Let me ask another way.

04:55.720 --> 04:57.850
Since you're such a sensitive person,

04:57.870 --> 04:59.000
can't you sense that

04:59.000 --> 05:02.130
Mr. Ji treats you differently
from how he treats others?

05:03.040 --> 05:03.920
So what?

05:04.000 --> 05:05.870
That depends on you.

05:05.870 --> 05:07.390
What do you think of it?

05:08.750 --> 05:11.160
I just got out of a failed marriage.

05:11.800 --> 05:13.060
I can't move on so soon.

05:13.390 --> 05:16.000
Stop limiting yourself, okay?

05:16.040 --> 05:19.240
Nowadays, it's not unusual
to date three people in a year.

05:19.720 --> 05:20.510
Let me tell you.

05:20.510 --> 05:22.870
A romantic relationship
is just like a baked sweet potato.

05:22.870 --> 05:24.600
You have to enjoy it while it's still hot.

05:24.600 --> 05:26.720
But it also depends on
the right time and place.

05:26.720 --> 05:29.120
For example,
if you're walking in a desert,

05:29.270 --> 05:31.190
almost dying of heat and thirst,

05:31.190 --> 05:32.620
and someone gives you
a baked sweet potato,

05:32.620 --> 05:34.480
wouldn't that choke you to death?

05:35.120 --> 05:37.270
It's the same for a romantic relationship.

05:37.270 --> 05:39.000
If the timing is wrong,

05:39.950 --> 05:42.350
even the best person
won't be the right one.

05:45.159 --> 05:46.190
Then, right now,

05:46.600 --> 05:49.130
do you still want to
start a new relationship?

06:07.180 --> 06:09.290
♪ I know at the start of every story ♪

06:10.250 --> 06:12.270
♪ They all feel somewhat the same ♪

06:14.140 --> 06:16.410
♪ Just never thought I would ♪

06:17.460 --> 06:19.370
♪ Fall for you so deeply ♪

06:21.190 --> 06:23.510
♪ Why did I have to lose myself? ♪

06:24.040 --> 06:26.270
♪ In the virtual world ♪

06:27.530 --> 06:33.050
♪ Unfinished dreams hurt the most ♪

06:34.470 --> 06:36.390
♪ Like a moth drawn to the flame ♪

06:36.870 --> 06:40.250
♪ Wandering aimlessly
through the night sky ♪

06:41.760 --> 06:43.350
♪ Until I met you ♪

06:44.150 --> 06:47.250
♪ Like fire that finally took my life ♪

06:47.830 --> 06:49.620
♪ I thought my deep devotion
and sincerity ♪

06:50.250 --> 06:51.909
♪ Would earn your eternal loyalty ♪

06:52.440 --> 06:53.630
♪ Because you are like a cloud ♪

06:54.070 --> 06:55.870
♪ I became a wisp of wind ♪

06:56.320 --> 06:59.320
♪ In the end, all the promises we made ♪

06:58.950 --> 07:00.190
That night...

06:59.540 --> 07:01.200
♪ Turned into nothing but emptiness ♪

07:02.100 --> 07:03.880
♪ Once, for your dream ♪

07:04.090 --> 07:05.780
♪ I gritted my teeth
and pushed myself forward ♪

07:06.560 --> 07:08.760
♪ Love really hurts ♪

07:07.700 --> 07:08.540
[That night]

07:09.990 --> 07:14.650
♪ I never thought I could be so brave ♪

07:14.480 --> 07:15.830
Are you asleep?

07:17.190 --> 07:25.480
♪ In the end, everything came to nothing ♪

07:18.930 --> 07:19.570
[Are you asleep?]

07:29.300 --> 07:30.220
[Miyu]

07:41.909 --> 07:43.650
[Miyu]

07:48.290 --> 07:48.850
Mr. Wei.

07:52.720 --> 07:53.680
Mr. Duan Jr.

07:55.450 --> 07:56.580
Sorry to bother you.

07:57.180 --> 07:58.070
Mr. Wei.

07:58.240 --> 07:59.800
What brings you here?

08:00.310 --> 08:02.190
The Chinese restaurant
will open tomorrow, won't it?

08:02.190 --> 08:03.430
I'm up here to give you a heads-up.

08:03.430 --> 08:05.240
We need to be on the same page.

08:08.000 --> 08:10.540
I heard you booked a large private room.

08:12.000 --> 08:13.130
What does that mean?

08:13.190 --> 08:14.790
I don't quite understand it.

08:14.800 --> 08:17.280
It's to celebrate the successful opening
of your hotel's Chinese restaurant.

08:17.280 --> 08:19.480
What's there to be uable to understand?

08:19.680 --> 08:20.870
Why are you putting in so much effort

08:20.870 --> 08:22.240
for that Ji Feng?

08:22.600 --> 08:24.310
You have everyone at your beck and call.

08:24.310 --> 08:26.160
In the end,
he might get all the spotlight.

08:26.160 --> 08:27.160
It's not worth it.

08:27.240 --> 08:28.360
Mr. Wei, you're thinking too much.

08:28.340 --> 08:32.440
[Purong Hotel]

08:28.360 --> 08:30.680
I've merely helped you set up a stage.

08:30.920 --> 08:32.669
As for how to perform this show tomorrow,

08:32.669 --> 08:35.330
it still depends on
which play you want to watch.

08:37.240 --> 08:38.200
I knew it.

08:38.200 --> 08:39.950
You and I have the same taste.

08:40.360 --> 08:41.159
Alright then.

08:41.200 --> 08:42.500
Since you have no dietary restrictions,

08:42.500 --> 08:43.789
I'll arrange it as usual.

08:43.789 --> 08:46.200
Mr. Duan Jr., let's wait and see.

08:46.720 --> 08:47.560
I'm leaving now.

08:47.290 --> 08:50.580
[Purong Hotel]

08:57.790 --> 09:02.510
[Staff Only]

09:03.670 --> 09:05.240
Tomorrow, the private room
in the Chinese restaurant

09:05.240 --> 09:06.770
will turn into a lion's den.

09:07.180 --> 09:09.120
I wonder what kind of shady characters

09:09.120 --> 09:11.050
Duan Aoxiang will bring over here.

09:11.900 --> 09:12.690
Mr. Ji,

09:12.720 --> 09:15.440
should we ask more people
to keep an eye on things tomorrow?

09:15.440 --> 09:16.670
I'll be on compensatory leave tomorrow.

09:16.670 --> 09:18.400
I can come over and help Qiaoqi.

09:19.200 --> 09:20.790
Alright. It's settled then.

09:20.790 --> 09:22.910
You'll be fully
in charge of the private room tomorrow.

09:22.910 --> 09:24.320
Let me know if anything happens.

09:24.320 --> 09:25.010
Okay.

09:26.360 --> 09:27.120
Let's go.

09:27.440 --> 09:28.640
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

09:54.440 --> 09:55.320
[Staff Only]

10:08.830 --> 10:10.410
[Food Storage Box]

10:14.030 --> 10:15.230
You really scared me!

10:15.790 --> 10:17.120
What are you doing here?

10:17.150 --> 10:19.510
I'm here to see you and the cured pork.

10:19.510 --> 10:20.200
My foot has just healed,

10:20.200 --> 10:21.660
and now you've hit my head.

10:22.080 --> 10:23.540
-I'm sorry.
-Are you okay?

10:23.630 --> 10:25.560
What's wrong? Is the meat alright?

10:25.910 --> 10:27.110
It's perfectly fine.

10:31.550 --> 10:33.720
What's wrong? Is there a problem?

10:40.200 --> 10:42.400
There's something wrong with the meat.

10:49.910 --> 10:52.510
Don't worry.
The cured pork will be there soon.

11:01.640 --> 11:03.960
I can't believe
there's a mole in the kitchen.

11:03.960 --> 11:05.840
When I catch this despicable scumbag,

11:05.840 --> 11:08.170
I'll stuff this meat right into his mouth.

11:08.400 --> 11:09.300
Wait!

11:16.670 --> 11:19.510
Since they were so kind
to give us the meat,

11:20.440 --> 11:22.570
wouldn't it be a waste to throw it away?

11:37.680 --> 11:41.020
[Welcome to Purong Chinese Restaurant]

11:43.550 --> 11:44.840
Come on, guys.

11:43.930 --> 11:44.720
[Purong Chinese Restaurant]

11:44.960 --> 11:46.910
Today is the first day

11:46.490 --> 11:48.190
[Purong Chinese Restaurant]

11:46.910 --> 11:48.270
of Purong Chinese Restaurant's reopening.

11:48.270 --> 11:50.330
Everyone, present a brand-new image

11:50.390 --> 11:51.840
to welcome all the upcoming guests.

11:51.840 --> 11:52.360
Okay?

11:52.550 --> 11:53.280
Okay!

11:53.550 --> 11:54.530
Mr. Yang.

11:54.790 --> 11:55.510
Mr. Ji.

11:55.710 --> 11:56.770
Thanks for coming.

11:57.320 --> 11:58.380
Congratulations.

11:58.630 --> 12:01.010
Today, I'm going to
taste the food carefully.

12:01.010 --> 12:03.460
Yes, you have to taste it carefully today.

12:04.080 --> 12:05.680
Stir-fried Eel with Eight Delicacies.

12:05.680 --> 12:07.630
Eleven plates of Shanghai Smoked Fish.

12:07.630 --> 12:09.960
Serve as many
Osmanthus Rice Cakes as we have.

12:09.960 --> 12:10.480
Sit.

12:14.640 --> 12:15.890
Fetch a high chair.

12:19.150 --> 12:19.910
Ms. Xu.

12:20.720 --> 12:22.750
I didn't expect Mr. Ji would send you here
to control the scene personally.

12:22.750 --> 12:24.030
I'm flattered, Mr. Duan.

12:24.030 --> 12:25.390
Today, we have so many guests here.

12:25.390 --> 12:27.420
It's my honor to serve everyone.

12:27.510 --> 12:28.440
Come in, please.

12:30.000 --> 12:30.880
Welcome.

12:31.000 --> 12:31.510
Please.

12:34.270 --> 12:35.440
The private room is already full.

12:35.440 --> 12:37.760
There are still six empty tables
in the main hall.

12:37.760 --> 12:38.360
Take care.

12:39.670 --> 12:41.300
Not a single table can be empty today.

12:41.300 --> 12:42.770
Ask our clerks to give the guests
in the HSKP Department

12:42.770 --> 12:44.230
some Chinese restaurant vouchers.

12:44.230 --> 12:44.870
Okay.

12:47.790 --> 12:48.990
Hello, Mr. Duan Jr.

12:49.200 --> 12:49.870
Mr. Duan Jr.

12:49.890 --> 12:51.360
-You guys are here, too.
-Mr. Duan Jr.

12:51.360 --> 12:52.440
Have a seat. Sit.

12:52.840 --> 12:53.870
Where is the Crab Roe Tofu?

12:53.870 --> 12:55.120
-Is it ready?
-Almost!

12:55.120 --> 12:57.240
The people upstairs
are pushing for Yan Du Xian.

12:57.240 --> 12:58.370
It'll be ready soon.

13:12.840 --> 13:13.510
Serve it.

13:18.910 --> 13:19.630
Luo!

13:19.840 --> 13:20.840
Come and help!

13:26.120 --> 13:27.880
Why are we changing it, Qiaoqi?

13:28.850 --> 13:30.850
We'll have a good show to watch soon.

13:38.960 --> 13:39.750
Zhi.

13:40.440 --> 13:41.630
How does this taste?

13:45.030 --> 13:46.270
Where did you purchase

13:46.130 --> 13:49.020
[Purong Hotel]

13:46.270 --> 13:47.600
this salted meat?

13:48.240 --> 13:49.550
It doesn't even taste right.

13:49.550 --> 13:52.410
Didn't the chef taste it
before the food was served?

13:56.320 --> 13:58.600
Is this what you call a signature dish?

13:56.420 --> 14:00.060
[Purong Hotel]

13:59.000 --> 14:00.330
It's so disappointing.

14:00.390 --> 14:01.320
Today, I've even

14:01.390 --> 14:02.990
specially invited Zhi here.

14:03.150 --> 14:04.950
In front of so many of my friends,

14:05.270 --> 14:07.670
how can I get out of
this awkward situation?

14:07.690 --> 14:13.310
[Purong Hotel]

14:07.880 --> 14:09.140
Well, my dear friends,

14:09.150 --> 14:10.720
it's my treat today.

14:10.910 --> 14:13.510
Now let's go to Kuanli Mingjue
across the street.

14:13.510 --> 14:14.630
The head chef there

14:14.630 --> 14:16.750
has prepared
the authentic Yan Du Xian for you all.

14:16.660 --> 14:17.890
[Purong Hotel]

14:16.870 --> 14:18.150
Oh, by the way,

14:18.150 --> 14:19.390
our head chef in Kuanli

14:19.390 --> 14:22.270
is Jia Shikun, who came from here.

14:22.440 --> 14:25.120
He's the famous Chef Jia
in the Shanghai Bund.

14:25.120 --> 14:26.320
His specialty dish

14:26.320 --> 14:27.410
happens to be

14:27.440 --> 14:28.250
Yan Du Xian.

14:30.760 --> 14:32.170
Mr. Duan, please wait.

14:33.390 --> 14:34.240
Everyone,

14:35.390 --> 14:36.480
please give me some time

14:36.480 --> 14:37.670
to say a few words.

14:38.030 --> 14:39.270
Please have a seat.

14:39.270 --> 14:40.080
Actually,

14:40.080 --> 14:42.240
that bowl of food you just ate

14:42.240 --> 14:44.730
wasn't our signature dish, Yan Du Xian.

14:45.320 --> 14:47.270
It was just a small interlude.

14:48.030 --> 14:49.000
As for the exact details

14:49.000 --> 14:50.390
of the story behind it,

14:50.390 --> 14:52.080
I'd like to invite you all to taste

14:52.080 --> 14:54.870
our real signature dish,
Yan Du Xian, first.

14:54.870 --> 14:56.130
And then I will tell you

14:56.360 --> 14:57.440
the whole story.

14:59.890 --> 15:00.590
Come on.

15:00.790 --> 15:01.520
Miyu.

15:12.550 --> 15:13.310
Be careful.

15:15.440 --> 15:16.400
Zhi.

15:16.420 --> 15:18.360
I'd like to invite you
to taste the Yan Du Xian

15:18.360 --> 15:20.120
which our head chef simmered
with the ingredients

15:20.120 --> 15:21.580
she personally selected.

15:22.020 --> 15:22.660
Please.

15:33.630 --> 15:34.550
This flavor...

15:35.510 --> 15:36.200
is so fresh,

15:36.550 --> 15:37.270
so wild

15:37.640 --> 15:38.330
and so strong.

15:38.330 --> 15:39.210
I like it.

15:40.110 --> 15:41.120
So previously...

15:41.550 --> 15:44.790
Previously, a distinguished guest

15:44.790 --> 15:47.050
heard that we would host a dinner
for VIPs today,

15:47.050 --> 15:50.230
so he specially brought us
a piece of salted meat last night.

15:50.230 --> 15:52.270
Then our general manager felt

15:52.270 --> 15:54.340
it would be ungracious
to refuse such kindness,

15:54.340 --> 15:55.670
so he asked us to use

15:55.670 --> 15:57.600
the best broth and the best ingredients

15:57.600 --> 15:59.270
to simmer this salted meat.

15:59.440 --> 16:00.910
Perhaps our capabilities are so limited

16:00.910 --> 16:03.480
that we really couldn't
handle such a precious gift.

16:03.480 --> 16:06.030
That's the cause
of what happened just now.

16:06.120 --> 16:07.030
I'm sorry

16:07.030 --> 16:08.550
to let you see this awkward situation.

16:08.550 --> 16:10.410
Who is this distinguished guest?

16:11.320 --> 16:13.030
It doesn't matter

16:13.030 --> 16:14.510
who this distinguished guest is.

16:14.510 --> 16:15.630
What's important is that

16:15.630 --> 16:16.280
Mr. Duan

16:16.440 --> 16:18.670
has invited you here today.

16:18.790 --> 16:21.080
Your sharp comment just now

16:21.080 --> 16:22.390
really gave us

16:22.390 --> 16:24.240
enough confidence and recognition.

16:24.240 --> 16:25.670
We are extremely grateful.

16:25.670 --> 16:28.550
It looks like this young lady
is really good at telling stories.

16:28.550 --> 16:29.840
I'm going to include this information

16:29.840 --> 16:31.120
in my review.

16:32.510 --> 16:35.510
Being able to read our hotel's own story

16:35.510 --> 16:37.770
in your food review column

16:37.840 --> 16:40.000
would be our greatest honor.

16:40.000 --> 16:41.390
Zhi, I'd also like to thank you

16:41.390 --> 16:43.790
for strongly recommending
our hotel's signature dish,

16:43.790 --> 16:45.510
Yan Du Xian.

16:52.200 --> 16:53.930
It looks like this Purong Hotel

16:54.030 --> 16:55.630
is still as good as ever.

16:58.510 --> 17:00.290
It's a time-honored brand after all.

17:00.290 --> 17:02.150
It really deserves its reputation.

17:02.150 --> 17:02.910
Let's eat.

17:02.910 --> 17:04.109
Let's all eat.

17:24.640 --> 17:26.040
Thanks. Enjoy your meal.

17:29.400 --> 17:30.920
Are you satisfied with the dishes?

17:30.920 --> 17:32.780
-They're good.
-Enjoy your meal.

17:35.750 --> 17:36.590
Ma'am,

17:36.920 --> 17:39.180
are you satisfied with the dishes today?

17:41.400 --> 17:43.400
They're great. I'm very satisfied.

17:43.920 --> 17:46.650
I won't disturb you then.
Please enjoy your meal.

18:00.350 --> 18:01.900
Chef Jia is asking

18:01.920 --> 18:03.510
when the guests will arrive.

18:03.510 --> 18:04.840
Why are you even asking?

18:05.070 --> 18:06.130
Can't you sense it?

18:06.330 --> 18:07.330
I got it, Mr. Duan.

18:09.820 --> 18:10.950
Come on, Mr. Duan Jr.

18:11.880 --> 18:12.880
Come on, Zhi.

18:12.990 --> 18:14.090
The food is good.

18:14.380 --> 18:15.340
Of course.

18:15.370 --> 18:16.810
Enjoy your meal.

18:21.880 --> 18:22.590
Mr. Wang.

18:23.030 --> 18:23.900
Thanks for coming.

18:23.900 --> 18:25.270
Let me know if you need anything.

18:25.270 --> 18:26.240
Thank you.

18:26.240 --> 18:27.170
Enjoy your meal.

18:31.630 --> 18:32.880
Everyone is eating, huh?

18:32.880 --> 18:33.960
Welcome.

18:34.880 --> 18:35.760
Zhi.

18:35.780 --> 18:36.780
How does it taste?

18:38.430 --> 18:42.710
The flavors of the four seasons
are all in these dishes.

18:44.260 --> 18:45.020
Is that so?

18:45.330 --> 18:46.090
Mr. Duan Jr.,

18:46.110 --> 18:48.370
it looks like you're all very satisfied.

18:48.510 --> 18:50.380
We're very satisfied. It's very good.

18:50.380 --> 18:51.510
It's really so good.

18:51.530 --> 18:53.330
Why don't you taste it yourself?

18:56.720 --> 18:57.580
Let me taste it.

19:01.620 --> 19:03.680
The flavor is indeed extraordinary.

19:07.510 --> 19:08.350
Enjoy your meal.

19:08.350 --> 19:09.110
Excuse me.

19:16.130 --> 19:16.930
Mr. Duan Jr.!

19:17.790 --> 19:18.590
Mr. Duan Jr.!

19:19.630 --> 19:20.110
Well...

19:21.200 --> 19:22.590
I thought you would understand

19:22.590 --> 19:23.750
my good intentions

19:23.750 --> 19:24.960
and help me.

19:25.270 --> 19:28.510
I didn't expect you to come here
and see how embarrassed I was.

19:28.510 --> 19:30.430
Mr. Duan Jr., you've misunderstood.

19:30.430 --> 19:31.920
I was also kept in the dark.

19:32.790 --> 19:34.070
I made arrangements.

19:34.090 --> 19:36.240
Who would have thought
it would turn out like this?

19:36.240 --> 19:37.090
Alright.

19:37.790 --> 19:39.670
Anyway, I've shown enough respect for you.

19:39.670 --> 19:41.130
And I've invited the VIPs.

19:41.530 --> 19:43.730
Then you'll have to pay for this meal.

19:46.390 --> 19:47.150
Mr. Duan Jr.!

19:50.410 --> 19:52.880
Let's drink to the successful opening
of the Chinese restaurant!

19:52.880 --> 19:54.550
Cheers!

19:59.880 --> 20:02.880
It's all thanks to your efforts today.

20:02.880 --> 20:05.400
Otherwise,
I would have ruined our reputation.

20:05.400 --> 20:06.880
Speaking of that guy, Guo Luda,

20:06.880 --> 20:08.610
I definitely won't let him off.

20:08.830 --> 20:11.310
As a dignified senior chef skilled in
both hot dishes and pastry making,

20:11.310 --> 20:13.310
how could he play dirty tricks on me
behind my back?

20:13.310 --> 20:14.440
It's a reasonable suspicion,

20:14.440 --> 20:15.510
but we have no solid evidence,

20:15.510 --> 20:17.640
so we still can't jump to conclusions.

20:17.790 --> 20:20.000
Everyone knows about the opening
of the Chinese restaurant.

20:20.000 --> 20:22.200
If someone is really hiding in the corner

20:22.200 --> 20:23.480
to cause trouble for us,

20:23.480 --> 20:25.410
it'll be hard to guard against him.

20:25.680 --> 20:27.590
So, Qiaoqi,

20:27.590 --> 20:30.440
I hope from now on, you can
think twice before taking action.

20:30.440 --> 20:31.640
Impulse is the devil.

20:31.880 --> 20:34.460
The kitchen isn't a place
just anyone can enter.

20:34.460 --> 20:35.220
Qiaoqi.

20:36.090 --> 20:39.250
You're the head chef
of the Chinese restaurant now.

20:39.590 --> 20:42.440
You have a clear view
of everything in the kitchen.

20:42.440 --> 20:45.510
No one has a broader perspective than you.

20:45.750 --> 20:47.070
At this time, if you slowly

20:47.070 --> 20:49.200
calm down and observe everyone,

20:49.960 --> 20:52.090
bad guys are all afraid of being exposed.

20:52.090 --> 20:54.220
The fox will definitely show its tail.

20:54.870 --> 20:56.240
Now that I've heard what you said,

20:56.240 --> 20:58.200
the swapping of the cured pork

20:58.880 --> 21:01.440
must have something to do
with Duan Aoxiang.

21:01.460 --> 21:02.860
I have that feeling, too.

21:03.030 --> 21:04.490
In the private room today,

21:04.590 --> 21:06.510
Mr. Duan almost took everyone on the spot

21:06.510 --> 21:08.030
straight to Kuanli.

21:08.030 --> 21:09.030
It was as if they had been

21:09.030 --> 21:10.550
prepared for it all along.

21:11.680 --> 21:13.830
That's consistent with the news
I've gathered.

21:13.830 --> 21:16.430
I've heard
in terms of Duan Aoxiang's banquet,

21:16.510 --> 21:19.110
Kuanli was also preparing for it
at the same time.

21:19.110 --> 21:21.110
I guess if we had made ourselves
laughingstocks here,

21:21.110 --> 21:23.480
they could just take everyone
straight to Kuanli.

21:23.480 --> 21:25.880
So fortunately,
we found out about it in time.

21:25.880 --> 21:27.830
Chef Jia sharpened his knife in vain.

21:27.830 --> 21:30.150
It's getting clearer
who caused this trouble.

21:30.150 --> 21:32.500
Duan Aoxiang, that wretched playboy.

21:32.920 --> 21:33.980
Speaking of which,

21:34.110 --> 21:34.680
today,

21:34.680 --> 21:37.310
although it looked like a good start,

21:38.000 --> 21:39.030
in fact, most of the guests

21:39.030 --> 21:40.920
were well-connected people
or relatives and friends.

21:40.920 --> 21:42.110
As for the rest, we just relied on

21:42.110 --> 21:44.150
discount coupons to create a buzz.

21:44.550 --> 21:45.880
There were still not many new guests.

21:45.880 --> 21:47.510
I don't know how things will be tomorrow.

21:47.510 --> 21:50.840
I've already asked the sales department
to print vouchers.

21:51.000 --> 21:52.310
Tell them to prepare more.

21:52.310 --> 21:54.720
If the situation is still not good
tomorrow morning,

21:54.720 --> 21:58.050
ask the HSKP Department
to give more vouchers to the guests.

21:58.200 --> 21:58.950
In short,

21:59.000 --> 22:01.270
the first three days after the opening
are just like a movie's

22:01.270 --> 22:02.750
opening weekend box office.

22:02.750 --> 22:04.510
Success or failure is crucial.

22:06.590 --> 22:07.280
Cheers.

22:09.480 --> 22:11.140
Looking forward to tomorrow.

22:17.090 --> 22:18.190
I'm starving.

22:18.510 --> 22:20.310
Why hasn't the food arrived yet?

22:35.030 --> 22:36.430
What's for dinner today?

22:38.240 --> 22:40.570
White Gourd Soup with Cured Pork and Kelp,

22:41.030 --> 22:42.690
Braised Rice with Cured Pork,

22:44.130 --> 22:45.720
Cured Pork with Tofu

22:46.240 --> 22:48.500
and Cured Pork with Agrocybe Mushrooms.

22:49.030 --> 22:50.830
Alright. All the dishes are served.

22:50.830 --> 22:51.800
Please enjoy your meal.

22:51.800 --> 22:52.350
Wait.

22:55.670 --> 22:56.260
What...

22:56.750 --> 22:57.680
does this mean?

22:59.070 --> 23:01.640
Thank you for inviting
a table full of gourmets today

23:01.640 --> 23:03.380
to support our Chinese restaurant.

23:03.380 --> 23:05.980
This is a luxury dinner
specially made for you.

23:07.200 --> 23:08.510
What's this smell?

23:08.880 --> 23:10.110
Are you trying to poison me?

23:10.110 --> 23:11.270
Of course not.

23:11.550 --> 23:13.510
This all-cured-pork feast

23:13.720 --> 23:15.240
was prepared with the cured pork
our mysterious VIP

23:15.240 --> 23:17.030
had sent to our kitchen.

23:17.270 --> 23:19.270
These are top-notch ingredients.

23:19.400 --> 23:21.110
How would anyone else deserve to eat them?

23:21.110 --> 23:24.770
From now on, it'll be a special offer
for this presidential suite.

23:24.880 --> 23:27.610
I won't disturb you then.
Please enjoy your meal.

23:28.550 --> 23:29.150
By the way,

23:29.770 --> 23:31.030
it's more than enough.

23:34.120 --> 23:35.480
Just wait, you all!

23:52.560 --> 23:53.720
There are so many people.

23:53.720 --> 23:55.030
Are they all waiting for tables?

23:55.030 --> 23:56.020
Yes, they are.

23:56.050 --> 23:57.050
Li! Li!

23:57.770 --> 23:59.980
Tell the kitchen to hurry up
and get ready.

23:59.980 --> 24:00.790
Okay.

24:05.480 --> 24:06.110
Come on!

24:06.290 --> 24:07.540
The soup is ready!

24:27.380 --> 24:28.680
Can the Yan Du Xian be served now?

24:28.680 --> 24:29.310
Yes, it can.

24:29.310 --> 24:30.680
Okay. Let's go.

24:31.350 --> 24:32.030
Waiter!

24:32.030 --> 24:33.480
I've been calling for a long time.
Where's the waiter?

24:33.480 --> 24:34.440
Coming soon.

24:35.250 --> 24:37.450
Waiter, we want to order more food here!

24:40.400 --> 24:41.330
What a good meal!

24:41.550 --> 24:42.230
Let's go.

24:42.680 --> 24:43.640
Is there anyone else who wants to order?

24:43.640 --> 24:44.920
I want a portion of Yan Du Xian.

24:44.920 --> 24:46.350
To order more food,
please click on this first.

24:46.350 --> 24:47.030
Come here!

24:47.030 --> 24:48.430
Serve this table! Hurry!

24:48.590 --> 24:50.150
Waiter, I want more drinks.

24:50.240 --> 24:51.110
We still have one dish
that hasn't been served yet.

24:51.110 --> 24:51.790
Hurry up.

24:52.640 --> 24:54.030
Coming soon.

24:58.090 --> 24:59.230
Go help them now.

25:03.490 --> 25:05.550
Waiter, is our food ready?

25:05.550 --> 25:06.510
Coming soon.

25:08.270 --> 25:09.270
How does it taste?

25:09.270 --> 25:10.260
It's quite good.

25:10.280 --> 25:11.220
Enjoy your meal.

25:17.530 --> 25:18.770
When will the Eight-Treasure Duck
be ready?

25:18.770 --> 25:20.510
If the Braised Fish Tail
still isn't ready, the guest will leave.

25:20.510 --> 25:21.310
Coming!

25:22.380 --> 25:23.470
How is it today?

25:23.490 --> 25:24.600
Is the business outside very good?

25:24.600 --> 25:25.730
It's more than good.

25:25.760 --> 25:27.620
It's booming. A roaring success.

25:28.730 --> 25:29.740
Everyone!

25:30.090 --> 25:31.600
Did you hear that?

25:31.920 --> 25:33.260
The business is booming today.

25:33.260 --> 25:35.520
Let's all hurry up.

25:35.700 --> 25:37.100
The guests like our food.

25:37.120 --> 25:39.110
Whatever skills you have,

25:39.110 --> 25:40.240
show them all.

25:40.240 --> 25:41.240
Did you hear that?

25:41.260 --> 25:42.620
Yes!

25:46.350 --> 25:47.750
At this time, if you slowly

25:47.750 --> 25:49.760
calm down and observe everyone,

25:49.780 --> 25:51.480
bad guys are all afraid of being exposed.

25:51.480 --> 25:53.610
The fox will definitely show its tail.

25:55.200 --> 25:56.800
I'll emphasize this again.

25:56.930 --> 25:59.310
Today's Yan Du Xian is the top priority

25:59.340 --> 26:00.880
and plays the absolute key role.

26:00.880 --> 26:03.190
The clay pots are stewing on the stoves.

26:03.210 --> 26:05.670
The cured pork is frozen
in the storage room.

26:05.940 --> 26:08.090
Those who have sticky fingers
should stay away.

26:08.090 --> 26:09.750
If anyone dares to
cause trouble for me again,

26:09.750 --> 26:11.080
I'll teach him a lesson.

26:13.110 --> 26:14.310
Well, what do you mean?

26:14.310 --> 26:15.590
Who are you talking about?

26:15.590 --> 26:17.420
Li Qiaoqi, make it clear.

26:17.440 --> 26:18.840
Stop being sarcastic here.

26:18.840 --> 26:19.720
Mr. Guo.

26:19.900 --> 26:21.360
Why are you overreacting?

26:21.510 --> 26:23.040
Have I stepped on your tail?

26:24.270 --> 26:25.310
If I, Guo Luda,

26:25.310 --> 26:26.830
had ever touched your cured pork,

26:26.830 --> 26:29.030
I-I-I'd change my surname to yours, Li.

26:29.200 --> 26:30.400
Why are you always making

26:30.400 --> 26:31.830
sarcastic comments in this kitchen?

26:31.830 --> 26:32.960
When can you stop?

26:32.980 --> 26:33.880
If you don't like me,

26:33.880 --> 26:35.000
you can just fire me.

26:35.000 --> 26:37.270
If you want to
domineer over me and bully me,

26:37.270 --> 26:38.790
believe it or not,
I would perform a suplex on you.

26:38.790 --> 26:39.510
Come on!

26:39.510 --> 26:40.510
I'll do it now!

26:41.070 --> 26:41.930
I'll just do it!

26:42.100 --> 26:43.310
Guys!

26:43.310 --> 26:44.750
Calm down!

26:44.770 --> 26:45.830
The guests outside in the restaurant
are pushing for their food.

26:45.830 --> 26:47.830
They're about to tear the roof down.

26:48.140 --> 26:49.480
You can fight another day.

26:49.480 --> 26:49.920
Okay?

26:50.130 --> 26:50.880
Heroine.

26:51.310 --> 26:52.070
Good guy.

26:53.080 --> 26:56.740
You only know how to smooth things over
and talk like a bureaucrat.

26:57.330 --> 26:58.230
Calm down.

26:59.510 --> 27:01.460
Qiaoqi. Qiaoqi.

27:01.510 --> 27:03.170
Don't always be so emotional.

27:05.390 --> 27:07.420
I'm the one who's being unprofessional.

27:07.420 --> 27:08.700
Mr. Xue, I'm very busy.

27:08.730 --> 27:09.530
Excuse me.

27:12.890 --> 27:14.220
Everyone, work harder!

27:14.750 --> 27:15.510
Okay!

27:26.050 --> 27:27.920
Hello, how many tables are there
before my turn?

27:27.920 --> 27:29.270
There are five or six tables
before your turn.

27:29.270 --> 27:30.680
Please wait a bit longer.

27:30.680 --> 27:31.750
There are still five or six tables?

27:31.750 --> 27:33.410
Yes, please wait a bit longer.

27:34.510 --> 27:35.110
This way.

27:36.070 --> 27:38.200
This is the guest from Room 1815.

27:38.300 --> 27:39.370
Hello.

27:39.400 --> 27:41.960
Are you still planning to check out today?

27:42.000 --> 27:42.550
Yes.

27:42.990 --> 27:45.720
Isn't it fine
as long as I check out before 2:00 PM?

27:45.830 --> 27:46.550
2:00 PM

27:46.550 --> 27:48.500
is our deadline for late checkout.

27:48.750 --> 27:51.450
If there were no guests,
we could definitely make exceptions.

27:51.450 --> 27:54.300
But right now,
there are indeed guests waiting.

27:54.510 --> 27:55.880
It's not that I don't want to check out.

27:55.880 --> 27:56.750
The key is that

27:56.750 --> 27:59.270
I just don't know
when my number will be called,

27:59.270 --> 28:00.200
so I don't dare to leave

28:00.200 --> 28:01.800
and go back to pack my things.

28:02.680 --> 28:03.800
Do you think this is okay?

28:03.800 --> 28:05.290
I'll wait in line for you here.

28:05.290 --> 28:06.700
You can go back to pack your things first.

28:06.700 --> 28:08.700
Come down after you've checked out.

28:09.400 --> 28:10.640
Alright. Thank you.

28:10.660 --> 28:11.280
You're welcome.

28:11.280 --> 28:13.140
Then please come this way with me.

28:13.870 --> 28:14.790
Sorry for the trouble, Ms. Xu.

28:14.790 --> 28:15.590
It's my duty.

28:16.880 --> 28:17.880
This way, please.

28:22.410 --> 28:25.110
Luo Qingping, I'm handling something
at the Chinese restaurant.

28:25.110 --> 28:27.440
If anything happens upstairs,
let me know anytime.

28:27.440 --> 28:28.240
Roger that.

28:30.490 --> 28:31.620
Mr. Ji.

28:31.650 --> 28:33.540
Gao from the Purchasing Department

28:33.540 --> 28:35.260
is both inarticulate and bad-tempered.

28:35.260 --> 28:37.510
That's the reason why he loses out.

28:37.720 --> 28:39.650
Having worked on hotel finance
for so many years,

28:39.650 --> 28:41.240
he still doesn't understand
worldly wisdom.

28:39.980 --> 28:42.100
[Huang Chengmin]

28:41.590 --> 28:43.350
But he's a really good person

28:43.190 --> 28:45.690
[Xue Rui]

28:43.350 --> 28:45.510
and is absolutely loyal to our hotel.

28:45.510 --> 28:46.640
Mr. Ji, you can't just listen to

28:46.640 --> 28:48.750
the one-sided story of the whistleblowers.

28:47.460 --> 28:49.020
[Where are you?]

28:51.310 --> 28:52.240
Mr. Huang.

28:52.590 --> 28:54.350
We've already handed this matter over

28:54.350 --> 28:56.610
to the Business Management Department.

28:56.720 --> 28:58.520
I know you quite cherish talented people.

28:58.520 --> 28:59.470
I understand.

28:59.490 --> 29:01.810
But let's wait
for the investigation results.

29:01.810 --> 29:02.520
Okay?

29:13.950 --> 29:15.960
You can look at the menu
and order your food first.

29:15.960 --> 29:17.830
It will be quicker when you go in later.

29:17.830 --> 29:18.760
Okay. Thank you.

29:21.100 --> 29:23.070
You can bring two more tables
of guests up here.

29:23.070 --> 29:23.550
Okay.

29:23.550 --> 29:25.550
Guests over here, please follow me.

29:25.670 --> 29:27.280
This way, please.

29:48.640 --> 29:49.370
Are you okay?

29:49.810 --> 29:50.720
I'm sorry, Mr. Ji.

29:50.720 --> 29:51.320
I'm sorry.

29:51.550 --> 29:52.170
It's fine.

29:52.400 --> 29:53.110
Clean it up.

30:09.690 --> 30:10.930
Let me wipe it for you.

30:14.460 --> 30:15.350
Is it hot?

30:15.550 --> 30:16.470
It's fine.

30:26.670 --> 30:27.710
It's not very hot.

30:33.940 --> 30:34.580
By the way,

30:34.960 --> 30:36.560
why are there so many people
at the entrance?

30:36.560 --> 30:38.220
Did something happen inside?

30:39.590 --> 30:42.310
Nothing happened.
Business is just really good today.

30:42.310 --> 30:44.290
The guests are all lining up for tables.

30:44.290 --> 30:45.500
But don't worry.

30:45.640 --> 30:47.180
Mr. Xue is inside,

30:47.270 --> 30:48.720
and Qiaoqi is in the kitchen.

30:48.720 --> 30:49.750
Everything is arranged.

30:49.750 --> 30:51.730
It's just that the guests keep coming
one after another.

30:51.730 --> 30:52.590
How about this?

30:52.720 --> 30:53.830
Let's open up the coffee bar

30:53.830 --> 30:55.480
to the waiting guests as well.

30:55.480 --> 30:57.200
Good idea. I'll go right now.

30:57.200 --> 30:57.750
Okay.

31:17.000 --> 31:18.200
How is it going, guys?

31:18.590 --> 31:20.350
Can your wrists still handle it?

31:20.350 --> 31:21.310
Your wrists!

31:21.480 --> 31:22.920
Tell the guests outside

31:22.920 --> 31:24.640
there's not much Yan Du Xian left.

31:24.640 --> 31:26.830
How much is left exactly?

31:26.830 --> 31:27.640
Ya!

31:35.310 --> 31:36.510
Ten portions at most.

31:36.950 --> 31:38.950
Ten portions aren't enough, Ma'am.

31:39.110 --> 31:40.790
There are at least 50 tables outside.

31:40.790 --> 31:41.790
50 tables!

31:41.880 --> 31:43.920
That's why I'm asking you
to go out and inform them now.

31:43.920 --> 31:45.440
Tell them to come back tomorrow
if they want it.

31:45.440 --> 31:46.640
They've been waiting for over an hour.

31:46.640 --> 31:47.640
If I tell them to come back tomorrow,

31:47.640 --> 31:48.680
wouldn't I get beaten up?

31:48.680 --> 31:50.240
There's only one piece of meat left.

31:50.240 --> 31:52.160
Once it's eaten up, it'd be useless
even if you cut off my flesh.

31:52.160 --> 31:53.440
Do as I said
and just go out to tell them.

31:53.440 --> 31:54.160
The earlier you tell them,

31:54.160 --> 31:56.020
the lighter the beating would be.

32:01.810 --> 32:02.940
My crabs.

32:03.600 --> 32:04.800
They're overcooked.

32:20.110 --> 32:21.610
Are you two satisfied with our dishes?

32:21.610 --> 32:22.400
Not bad.

32:22.420 --> 32:23.240
Please enjoy your meal.

32:23.240 --> 32:24.040
Okay.

32:30.960 --> 32:32.310
Are you two satisfied with our dishes?

32:32.310 --> 32:33.350
They're good.

32:33.350 --> 32:34.880
Thank you. Enjoy your meal.

32:41.010 --> 32:42.490
You've seen the good news.

32:42.920 --> 32:44.480
Do you want to hear the bad news?

32:44.480 --> 32:45.010
Go ahead.

32:45.300 --> 32:47.170
We're running out of the cured pork.

32:47.170 --> 32:48.470
I called the Chunlai couple.

32:48.470 --> 32:50.280
They promised
to deliver the meat right away.

32:50.280 --> 32:52.390
You're just amazing.

32:53.440 --> 32:54.720
Everyone here can testify that

32:54.720 --> 32:56.030
both of our families
arrived at the same time

32:56.030 --> 32:57.180
and took numbers at the same time.

32:57.180 --> 32:59.310
It was just a matter
of who stretched out his hand first.

32:59.310 --> 33:01.550
Just now, we let you go first
when getting the numbers,

33:01.550 --> 33:02.640
but now you're trying to

33:02.640 --> 33:04.000
snatch food from our mouths.

33:04.000 --> 33:05.640
Just for a portion of Yan Du Xian,

33:05.640 --> 33:06.790
aren't you ashamed to do this?

33:06.790 --> 33:08.240
Then what do you mean?

33:08.240 --> 33:09.480
Are you not ashamed?

33:09.480 --> 33:11.880
Our number is clearly ahead of yours,

33:11.880 --> 33:14.030
but now you're forcing us to yield to you.

33:14.030 --> 33:15.500
Why should we agree?

33:15.550 --> 33:16.230
Then tell me

33:16.230 --> 33:16.960
what you mean.

33:16.960 --> 33:17.790
Stop arguing.

33:17.790 --> 33:18.480
Don't scare the children.

33:18.480 --> 33:19.960
Neither of the families is wrong.

33:19.960 --> 33:21.310
Failing to let everyone eat Yan Du Xian

33:21.310 --> 33:22.790
is the responsibility
of our Chinese restaurant.

33:22.790 --> 33:24.480
But there's really
nothing we can do today.

33:24.480 --> 33:25.830
-I'm really sorry.
-Um, wait.

33:25.830 --> 33:26.310
We...

33:26.310 --> 33:27.270
What about us?

33:27.480 --> 33:28.740
We've waited for so long.

33:28.740 --> 33:31.270
You advertised this Yan Du Xian
from the beginning.

33:31.270 --> 33:32.550
Now we're here,

33:32.550 --> 33:34.480
but you're telling us it's sold out.

33:34.480 --> 33:36.000
Isn't that a scam?

33:36.000 --> 33:36.720
I'm sorry.

33:36.720 --> 33:37.850
The key is that we...

33:38.960 --> 33:40.040
I have an idea.

33:41.030 --> 33:42.360
I'm so sorry, everyone.

33:42.790 --> 33:44.200
For the sake of the kids,

33:44.200 --> 33:46.130
please calm down.

33:46.240 --> 33:47.310
I have an idea.

33:47.310 --> 33:49.480
Let's see if both of your families

33:49.480 --> 33:51.130
could share one portion of Yan Du Xian.

33:51.130 --> 33:53.750
We can divide the large clay pot
into single-serving small bowls.

33:53.750 --> 33:55.480
In this way, both families can eat it.

33:55.480 --> 33:57.160
What's more, the single-serving bowls

33:57.160 --> 33:58.750
will be a bit cheaper.

33:59.720 --> 34:00.350
Additionally,

34:00.350 --> 34:02.790
we can also give you

34:02.790 --> 34:04.880
two free desserts for the two kids.

34:04.880 --> 34:06.680
In this way,
everyone can get to eat and drink,

34:06.680 --> 34:08.150
and the kids can even play together.

34:08.150 --> 34:09.150
Do you think that's okay?

34:09.150 --> 34:10.030
-Okay!
-Okay!

34:10.630 --> 34:11.690
That sounds great.

34:11.810 --> 34:13.429
Sir, please inform the kitchen.

34:13.429 --> 34:15.360
I'm going to kitchen to take a look.

34:16.280 --> 34:17.070
T-Then what about us?

34:17.070 --> 34:17.920
What about us?

34:17.920 --> 34:19.230
We want to eat Yan Du Xian, too.

34:19.230 --> 34:20.110
I'm sorry.

34:20.110 --> 34:22.230
The situation today is really so special.

34:22.230 --> 34:24.230
I apologize to you all here first.

34:26.710 --> 34:27.760
Professor Liu?

34:27.760 --> 34:30.150
The two of us usually
can't eat up a whole portion anyway.

34:30.150 --> 34:31.710
If anyone agrees,

34:31.710 --> 34:34.710
we don't mind
sharing a portion of Yan Du Xian with him.

34:34.810 --> 34:36.690
We can change to small portions, too.

34:36.690 --> 34:37.949
Thank you, Professor Liu.

34:37.949 --> 34:38.989
Thank you all.

34:40.440 --> 34:41.710
How about this, everyone?

34:41.710 --> 34:43.360
Then I'll ask this lady

34:43.360 --> 34:44.710
to count up how many people

34:44.710 --> 34:46.070
are willing to share Yan Du Xian.

34:46.070 --> 34:47.880
Then I'll go back to the restaurant

34:47.880 --> 34:49.630
and ask the guests
whose dishes haven't been served yet

34:49.630 --> 34:50.630
to see if anyone wants to spare

34:50.630 --> 34:52.190
more servings to share with you.

34:52.190 --> 34:53.590
Do you think that's okay?

34:54.030 --> 34:55.949
I think it's okay.
The manager really has a way.

34:55.949 --> 34:57.810
Wait a moment. I'll be right back.

34:57.990 --> 34:59.190
Mr. Xue! Mr. Xue!

35:00.220 --> 35:01.760
The delivery truck is already on its way.

35:01.760 --> 35:03.440
It will arrive at the hotel at 3 PM.

35:03.440 --> 35:05.170
Just wait to receive the goods.

35:07.950 --> 35:09.080
Then what about now?

35:09.360 --> 35:10.630
There are less than 10 portions
of Yan Du Xian left.

35:10.630 --> 35:12.760
A bunch of guests are waiting outside.

35:15.920 --> 35:18.390
Give them more discounts.

35:18.420 --> 35:20.330
Keep the guests no matter what.

35:20.960 --> 35:21.800
Besides Yan Du Xian,

35:21.800 --> 35:23.860
we have many other excellent dishes.

35:24.230 --> 35:25.820
Only when the guests sit down

35:25.820 --> 35:27.680
will they know our capabilities.

35:27.940 --> 35:28.720
Ms. Xu.

35:28.920 --> 35:30.000
How's it going outside?

35:30.000 --> 35:31.710
I've already discussed it with the guests.

35:31.710 --> 35:33.760
They're all willing to
exchange large pots for small bowls

35:33.760 --> 35:35.590
and share Yan Du Xian with others.

35:35.590 --> 35:37.320
I'm here to ask
how many tables in the restaurant

35:37.320 --> 35:39.320
haven't been served Yan Du Xian yet.

35:40.040 --> 35:42.310
If three more tables are willing to share,

35:42.310 --> 35:44.420
all the guests outside
will be able to eat Yan Du Xian.

35:44.420 --> 35:45.420
That's great.

35:45.440 --> 35:47.480
Go out and help the kitchen
communicate with the guests.

35:47.480 --> 35:48.680
I'll do it right away.

35:48.710 --> 35:51.630
You can help me
discuss with the management department

35:51.630 --> 35:52.760
the pricing
for a small portion of Yan Du Xian.

35:52.760 --> 35:53.370
Okay.

35:58.210 --> 36:00.010
Thanks for your hard work, Miyu.

36:02.880 --> 36:03.680
What's wrong?

36:05.890 --> 36:06.600
Nothing.

36:20.320 --> 36:21.000
Yummy!

36:21.000 --> 36:22.180
So fresh!

36:22.880 --> 36:23.960
Really delicious!

36:24.030 --> 36:24.670
Very good!

36:24.670 --> 36:25.320
Yummy!

36:31.960 --> 36:32.840
So good.

36:32.840 --> 36:33.480
Delicious.

36:33.480 --> 36:34.540
Really delicious.

36:45.150 --> 36:46.210
This feels so good!

36:46.920 --> 36:48.800
I haven't worked this hard in years.

36:48.800 --> 36:49.510
Really.

36:57.370 --> 36:58.320
Delicious.

36:58.400 --> 37:00.660
Once again, Qiaoqi's cooking has impro-

37:02.990 --> 37:04.280
When the Chinese restaurant was closed,

37:04.280 --> 37:06.230
I really wanted to die.

37:06.670 --> 37:09.150
I didn't expect the business would be
so good once it opened

37:09.150 --> 37:10.800
and everything would go so smoothly.

37:10.800 --> 37:12.000
Mr. Ji, you've helped me

37:12.000 --> 37:13.400
solve the cured pork problem twice.

37:13.400 --> 37:16.000
You're truly the cured pork superman
of our hotel.

37:16.000 --> 37:16.510
No, no, no.

37:16.510 --> 37:17.430
Don't call me that.

37:17.430 --> 37:18.360
It sounds weird.

37:20.760 --> 37:22.800
Speaking of cured pork,
I haven't asked you guys yet.

37:22.800 --> 37:24.550
When we went to Linglong Town previously,

37:24.550 --> 37:26.160
after Qiaoqi and I left,

37:26.230 --> 37:27.280
how did you two

37:27.280 --> 37:28.440
spend that night on the island?

37:28.440 --> 37:30.630
It seemed to rain quite heavily that day.

37:30.630 --> 37:31.960
Did the ferry even stop?

37:36.320 --> 37:37.710
Why are you so gossipy?

37:37.710 --> 37:39.150
Just eat your meat.

37:41.000 --> 37:41.770
I'm curious.

37:43.440 --> 37:44.780
By the way, speaking of which,

37:44.780 --> 37:46.440
the extent to which our restaurant
was full up today

37:46.440 --> 37:47.770
was indeed surprising.

37:47.890 --> 37:49.290
At first, I was worried

37:49.310 --> 37:51.870
whether someone
was trying to cause trouble

37:51.900 --> 37:54.030
and complain about
the dishes or something.

37:54.030 --> 37:56.280
But later, it didn't seem to be the case.

37:56.880 --> 37:59.630
As you said, good wine needs no bush.

38:00.030 --> 38:01.510
But don't you think this happened

38:01.510 --> 38:03.170
too quickly and too suddenly?

38:03.720 --> 38:04.990
I know why.

38:07.590 --> 38:09.050
During the daytime today,

38:09.110 --> 38:10.440
I heard many guests

38:10.440 --> 38:12.040
mentioning someone's name.

38:12.190 --> 38:13.840
I guess it must be because of her.

38:13.840 --> 38:14.710
-Who?
-Who?

38:15.880 --> 38:17.030
Dianjiangchun.

38:17.230 --> 38:18.590
Who is Dianjiangchun?

38:18.590 --> 38:19.920
You don't even know her?

38:21.360 --> 38:24.230
She's
a travel and restaurant-exploring blogger,

38:24.230 --> 38:25.880
who has been very active in recent years.

38:25.880 --> 38:27.190
For any restaurant she visits,

38:27.190 --> 38:28.710
if she gives it a good review,

38:28.710 --> 38:30.440
its popularity will soar.

38:30.840 --> 38:33.230
Dianjiangchun
really visited our Chinese restaurant.

38:33.230 --> 38:34.230
See? I told you so.

38:34.590 --> 38:36.150
I-Is this the blogger

38:36.150 --> 38:37.230
you liked so much before?

38:37.230 --> 38:38.400
Yes, it's her.

38:38.400 --> 38:41.140
She has 23,780,000 followers.

38:42.070 --> 38:42.880
Forget it. Don't look.

38:42.880 --> 38:43.760
You only have over 100 followers.

38:43.760 --> 38:44.790
Don't let it get on your nerves.

38:44.790 --> 38:45.850
Look what she said.

38:46.400 --> 38:49.920
The fragrance of spring
that cannot be missed

38:50.110 --> 38:53.610
is all in the Yan Du Xian of Purong Hotel.

38:54.320 --> 38:55.400
Such a review

38:55.760 --> 38:57.710
has saved us so much on advertising costs.

38:57.710 --> 38:58.320
Look.

38:58.320 --> 39:01.030
We've really met our lucky star.

39:02.040 --> 39:03.130
[Dianjiangchun]

39:05.390 --> 39:06.510
[Dianjiangchun]

39:06.540 --> 39:08.080
[Always on the road
recording the flavors of the mortal world]

39:09.000 --> 39:09.580
Cheers!

39:09.710 --> 39:10.680
Cheers!

39:11.800 --> 39:12.930
Let's drink a toast.

39:13.050 --> 39:13.740
Cheers.

39:25.400 --> 39:27.230
Let me treat you to skewers
somewhere else.

39:27.230 --> 39:29.410
We've just eaten.
Why should we have skewers?

39:29.410 --> 39:32.270
-Xu Miyu.
-Skewers taste differently from dinner.

39:38.270 --> 39:39.190
Do you have time?
